metadata.name: Digital Only Love on the Blockchain
metadata.description: The Love on the Blockchain earrings are a signature POCHE piece that represent the center of physical and spiritual being. The illuminating gold heart is a symbol of love but also a source of wisdom, compassion, and devotion. These earrings serve as a tribute to the ongoing crisis in Ukraine and are an everyday reminder to lead with your heart and hold empathy for others. 15% of primary sale proceeds will be donated to The Ukraine Emergency Response Fund. Note: The Digital Love on the Blockchain earrings exist only in the digital world.

attributes.value: 925 Silver, 18K Gold & Rhodium plating, 10.6 g, 3.6 cm
